{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idb527005c-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d","identifier":"/us/usc/t6/s484a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"484a"},"text":"§ 484a.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Reciprocal information sharing","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Acting in accordance with a bilateral or multilateral arrangement, the Secretary, in the Secretary’s discretion and on the basis of reciprocity, may provide information from the National Sex Offender Registry relating to a conviction for a sex offense against a minor (as such terms are defined in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t34/s20911"},"text":"section 20911 of title 34","children":[],"tail":") to a foreign government upon the request of the foreign government, and may receive comparable information from the foreign government."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idb527005d-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/296/tVIII/s895"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–296, title VIII, § 895","children":[],"tail":", as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/347/tIII/s323/a/1/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–347, title III, § 323(a)(1)(B)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2023-01-05"},"text":"Jan. 5, 2023","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/136/6207"},"text":"136 Stat. 6207","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idb527005e-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idb527005f-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note